data.description: Beautifully upgraded townhome with garage,  walking distance to beach. No detail was spared in this unit, from the coordinating furniture to the Italian tile with Schluter flooring underneath, the sound proofing of the walls and waterfall quartz countertops. Holiday isle has been a long time favorite for many reasons. Water enthusiasts hit the jackpot here. Holiday Isle offers easy access to some of the most spectacular water activities in the region. Whether it's deep-sea fishing, jet skiing, paddleboarding, or simply splashing in the emerald waters, there's no shortage of aquatic adventures. Experience the magic of Holiday Isle in Destin. A place where every day feels like a vacation day.  Holiday Isle is a favorite spot for travelers seeking paradise on the Emerald Coast Oversized garage to hold 2 cars or extra storage space for owner's items and beach/water toys.
